modelling approach in conjunction with wildfire power-law
frequency-area scaling exponent beta to calibrate the model. Parameters
describing the role of soil Moisture on vegetation dynamics are also
found to significantly influence land-cover change. Recent improvements
in understanding the role of soil moisture and wildfire fuel loads at
the landscape-level will drive advances in Mediterranean LFSMs. (C)
2009 Elsevier Ltd. All rights reserved.},
